OL,7,FThe family of a young mum murdered by
OL,8,Fher jealous ex are demanding answers
OL,9,Ffrom the Home Office about why it had
OL,10,Ffailed to deport him - despite him
OL,11,Fbeing an illegal immigrant who had
OL,12,Falready been jailed for attacking a
OL,13,Fwoman.
OL,15,FMother-of-two Perseverance Ncube, 35,
OL,16,Fwas chased from her home in and called
OL,17,F999. But her ex-partner Obert Moyo
OL,18,Fcaught up with her and stabbed through
OL,19,Fthe heart with a meat skewer.
