OL,7,FAs she was dying, her children, aged
OL,8,F10 and 12, lay with her and prayed for
OL,9,Fher life after bravely fighting him
OL,10,Foff when he had broken into their
OL,11,Fhouse in Dukesgate Grove, Little
OL,12,FHulton, on 10 November 2023.
OL,14,FMoyo, 46, of Pennington Road, , had
OL,15,Finitially denied murder but on the
OL,16,Ffirst day of his trial at Crown Court.
OL,18,FHe was jailed for life and ordered to
OL,19,Fserve a minimum of 27 years before
OL,20,Fbecoming eligible for parole.
