OL,7,FOn the steps of court after sentence
OL,8,Fhad been passed, Det Sgt Fiona Manning
OL,9,Fof , said the life sentence would
OL,10,Fnever bring Ms Ncube - known as Percy
OL,11,F- back to her family.
OL,13,FDet Sgt Fiona Manning of GMP speaking
OL,14,Foutside court.
OL,16,FShe added: "Percy's family deserve
OL,17,Fanswers, basically, from the Home
OL,18,FOffice as to why this man - as
OL,19,Fdangerous as Moyo was - was allowed to
OL,20,Flive in this country illegally for
OL,21,Fover 20 years.
