OL,7,F"Had Moyo been deported, Percy's
OL,8,Fchildren would still have a mother."
OL,10,FAlso speaking outside court, Det Ch
OL,11,FInsp Gina Brennand had said Moyo had
OL,12,Fstalked Ms Ncube for several months
OL,13,Fbefore killing her. This not not been
OL,14,Freported to the police but had been
OL,15,Frecorded on his immigration electronic
OL,16,Fmonitoring tag - fitted by the Home
OL,17,FOffice because he was an overstayer in
OL,18,Fthe UKand on CCTV.
