OL,7,FShe said in the hours before the
OL,8,Fattack, Moyo had gone to a filling
OL,9,Fstation to buy a can of pterol, having
OL,10,Falready himself with knives, a hammer
OL,11,Fand meat skewers. He planned to use
OL,12,Fthe petrol can to burn the house down
OL,13,Fafter killing her, she said.
OL,15,FDet Ch Insp Gina Brennad speaking
OL,16,Fafter Moyo had been jailed for life.
OL,18,FAfter stabbing Ms Ncube, he 'calmly'
OL,19,Fwalked away, disposing of the murder
OL,20,Fweapon, his mobile phone and
OL,21,Felectronic tag.
