OL,7,F"Moyo was an illegal immigrant. He was
OL,8,Fon prison licence, having served a 14-
OL,9,Fyear term for a violent offence
OL,10,Fagainst another woman. He is a danger
OL,11,Fto women."
OL,13,FManchester Crown Court heard Ms NCube
OL,14,Fand Moyo had been in a relationship
OL,15,Ffor about 18 months, but that Ms Ncube
OL,16,Fhad ended it after learning he had
OL,17,Fbeen seeing other women.
