OL,7,FDespite Ms Ncube telling him 'in no
OL,8,Funcertain terms' that their
OL,9,Frelationship was over after she met a
OL,10,Fnew partner, Moyo began turning up
OL,11,Foutside her home and 'stalking' her.
OL,13,FAt the time of the murder, Moyo was on
OL,14,Flicence having been released from
OL,15,Fprison for a brutal attack on another
OL,16,Fex-partner. He had been jailed for 14
OL,17,Fyears after attacking the woman with a
OL,18,Fknife and strangling her.
