OL,7,FHeartbreaking statements were read in
OL,8,Fcourt on behalf of her children.
OL,9,FAddressing Moyo, Ms Ncube's daughter
OL,10,Fsaid: "I just want to say you ruined
OL,11,Fmy whole life. You stole my mum from
OL,12,Fme. If you don't care I hope you get a
OL,13,Flife sentence. I really thought you
OL,14,Fwere like a father to me, but you're
OL,15,Fnot.
OL,17,F"I don't even know you anymore. I hate
OL,18,Fyou."
