OL,7,FHer son said he experiences a 'burning
OL,8,Fpain' every day without his mother. "I
OL,9,Fmiss her, I miss being able to hug
OL,10,Fher, being able to walk to her," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"I blame myself, believing I could and
OL,14,Fshould have done more. Bargaining like
OL,15,Fgiving my life, or an arm or a leg for
OL,16,Fher. He viciously attacked a woman who
OL,17,Fdid nothing wrong. He could have just
OL,18,Fmoved on."
