OL,7,FIn a message to his late mother, the
OL,8,Fboy added: "Mum, I miss you. I will
OL,9,Falways love you."
OL,11,FSentencing, Judge Patrick Field KC
OL,12,Fsaid of the children: "Their loss is
OL,13,Fincalculable. What they witnessed was
OL,14,Futterly terrible."
