OL,7,FHe told Moyo, of Pennington Road,
OL,8,FBolton, who sat with his head in his
OL,9,Fhands throughout the hearing: "This
OL,10,Fwas a calculated, premeditated, brutal
OL,11,Fand wicked offence. I am sure to the
OL,12,Fappropriate standard that you intended
OL,13,Fto kill Ms Ncube."
OL,15,FDefending, Dafydd Enoch KC said Moyo
OL,16,Fwas suffering from 'severe mental
OL,17,Fhealth difficulties' at the time. "He
OL,18,Fhas a real problem with the break up
OL,19,Fof relationships." he said of Moyo.
